OL,5, Many US newspapers including the       
OL,6, Washington Post have dropped the       
OL,7, long-running Dilbert cartoon strip     
OL,8, after its creator made racist comments.
OL,10,FIn a video on YouTube, Scott Adams, who
OL,11,Fis white, said black Americans were    
OL,12,Fpart of a "hate group" and that white  
OL,13,Fpeople should "get the hell away" from 
OL,14,Fthem.                                  
OL,16,FMr Adams, 65, later acknowledged that  
OL,17,Fhis career was destroyed.              
OL,19,FHe said most of his income would be    
OL,20,Fgone by next week.                     
